          A case was defined as a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">resident</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">San Francisco</ENAMEX> with
          <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">AIDS</ENAMEX> who was reported to the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">San Francisco</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Department of</ENAMEX>
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Public Health</ENAMEX> with a <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">laboratory</ENAMEX>-confirmed, positive stool
